Repost from @conservationorg I’m super excited to be a part of this beautiful project. It is an honor. Mahalo @savethewavescoalition @surfconservation for protecting our waves Aloha j
—
“What do you think I can do to your currents, your coastlines, your climate? My requirements are simple. Stop stripping the forests that keep my water clean, stop filling the atmosphere with dead carbon and keep your plastic to yourself. Work with me now, before it’s too late. I’ll keep coming, I am the wave.”

Aquaman actor, Native Hawaiian and ocean sustainability advocate Jason Momoa (@prideofgypsies) joins Conservation International’s award-winning Nature is Speaking series as The Wave. #NatureisSpeaking

@savethewavescoalition @surfconservation @taylorsteele

node.text:
I just found out this heartbreaking news. All my Aloha to this beautiful Ohana  Love u baby boy rest in piece  You will live in my heart  I dedicate aquaman 2 to you lil angel  Aloha UNKO Aquaman 

Repost from @wcvb5
•
Our hearts go out to the family and friends of Danny Sheehan, an 8-year-old from #Marshfield who has died of brain cancer. 💔 His love of Aquaman prompted a special call from the actor who portrays the superhero, Jason Momoa. Rest in peace, Danny. 🔱 To learn more about Danny’s life, click the link in our bio. #RIP #4TheLoveofDanny #Massachusetts #hero #Aquaman @prideofgypsies

node.text: i’ve worked really hard to support and be creative for the companies i love and believe in  it goes without saying that i have a massive passion for LEICA @leicacamerausa  the M2 present was unreal it’s my favourite film camera. but most importantly i got a personal note from the president ceo  unko mike that means just as much.  mahalo for the birthday wishes. and all my aloha to the leica team  @kiran.karnani  i’m very grateful aloha j
